## Common Patterns
- **401/403**: middleware order, JWT expiry, CSRF on `/oidc/login`, session cookie `Secure`/`SameSite` in local dev
- **OIDC redirect mismatch**: `redirect_uri` vs registered client
- **Session lost**: Redis TTL, `iam_session` cookie domain/path, [docs/features/SSO_SESSION.md](../../docs/features/SSO_SESSION.md)
- **Goroutine leak**: missing context cancellation on outbound HTTP
- **Migration drift**: `atlas.sum` out of sync — run `make migrate-hash`
